  "title": "Ops Admin with AutoCAD",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>· Prepare technical drawings as per project and product requirements using drafting (CAD) software</p><p>· Follow through any modification to the project and product requirements and update drawings accordingly</p><p>· Work closely with all relevant parties including Operations teams to ensure drawings are feasible and effectively translated into products using CNC machines</p><p>· Coordinate for Sales Order Processing</p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><p>· Candidate must possess at least \"N\" Level with Professional Certificate/NiTEC, Diploma/Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma in any field</p><p>· At least 1 Year(s) of working experience as a drafter – experience in the stone or related industry will be an advantage</p><p>· Required Skill(s): Microsoft Office, Autocad (CAD)</p><p>· Possess positive attitude and able to work in a fast-paced environment</p>",
